{"TopicId":201855,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"How close can you make it to the sun?","CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T14:20:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T14:20:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey, I\u2019m Matt.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you want, you should try and cram those radiators together and send a screenshot of how close you can get to the sun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave fun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Single stage to ocean","CreatedById":210256,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T15:46:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can actually get to a few thousand meters of sun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T15:52:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have the Beyond Home planet pack, which has a system with 2 suns. So my goal is to try to make it in between the two suns.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n(Without burning up of course)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JcoolTheShipbuilder","CreatedById":204576,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T16:52:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223957734\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201855\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618933942\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211240\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n59 minutes ago, Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have the Beyond Home planet pack, which has a system with 2 suns. So my goal is to try to make it in between the two suns.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Without burning up of course)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou may want heat shields on both sides. Don\u2019t use ablative shields\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T16:54:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I\u2019ll put a shield of radiators around the craft, and also have huge heat shields as another line of defense.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T16:54:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223957730\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201855\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618933596\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022210256\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Single stage to ocean\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Single stage to ocean said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can actually get to a few thousand meters of sun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd he/she is inviting people to try it and show their attempts. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T17:17:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCorrect\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002227914\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/27914-vanamonde/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Vanamonde\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0. \u00A0I bet somebody will post soon. I\u2019m working on my own\u00A0mission now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-20T17:17:34Z\u0022 title=\u002204/20/2021 05:17  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 20, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EGrammar correction\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-20T21:18:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/gr3CldN\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/gr3CldN\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002264.00\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 alt=\u0022AHb3ubg.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/AHb3ubg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is probably the closest that you can go to the Sun without aerodynamic exploits\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-20T21:20:34Z\u0022 title=\u002204/20/2021 09:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 20, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by camacju\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Single stage to ocean","CreatedById":210256,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T08:54:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwhat you have an energy flow of 400,000\u002B EC a sec, that can power 50,000 ions at full power. what.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T09:28:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCrikey, that\u0027s impressive. I had no idea that was possible.\u00A0What\u0027s your secret? Just massive, massive radiators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T13:41:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhelperdude","CreatedById":204462,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T13:55:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223957734\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201855\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618933942\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211240\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have the Beyond Home planet pack, which has a system with 2 suns. So my goal is to try to make it in between the two suns.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Without burning up of course)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndo you want to go to the uganda knuckles barycenter? DO IT xD!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T14:03:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223958217\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201855\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619013323\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022204462\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starhelperdude\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, Starhelperdude said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ndo you want to go to the uganda knuckles barycenter? DO IT\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe I\u2019ll try it later... with NO Kerbals involved.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-21T14:09:59Z\u0022 title=\u002204/21/2021 02:09  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 21, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T14:16:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223958140\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201855\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618997291\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022167629\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Brikoleur\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Brikoleur said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust massive, massive radiators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat, and what looks like a highly eccentric orbit, to spend less than 20s near \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Periapsis\u0022\u003EPe\u003C/abbr\u003E. Gives the pod 75 yrs to cool down before the next pass. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T14:16:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167629-brikoleur/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022167629\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/167629-brikoleur/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Brikoleur\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0yes, you just need a fair amount of /\\v, and a small craft with GIANT radiators.\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223958230\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201855\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619014580\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022152460\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022swjr-swis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, swjr-swis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat, and what looks like a highly eccentric orbit, to spend less than 20s near \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Periapsis\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Periapsis\u0022\u003EPe\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E. Gives the pod 75 yrs to cool down before the next pass. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame time\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T15:14:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA secret nobody\u0027s probably realized is that my time warp is at 100X which is a lot better for cooling. It\u0027s because at 100X time warp the heat calculations are done as if the craft is a single part, massively improving heat conduction between parts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lt_Duckweed","CreatedById":201466,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T15:39:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think that keeping in the spirit of the challenge would require using 1x timewarp at periapsis.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn 1x time warp, the closest you can get without resorting to exploits is something like 150,000-200,000 km from the surface.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith exploits you can get all the way to the atmosphere:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022 data-embed-src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Dej-zDeZqec?feature=oembed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-04-21T15:41:00Z\u0022 title=\u002204/21/2021 03:41  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00223 yr\u0022\u003EApril 21, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by Lt_Duckweed\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-21T16:41:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was wondering when you\u0027d turn up. With exploits allowed you can go to -250m on kerbol\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Single stage to ocean","CreatedById":210256,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-22T05:34:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats not true, even with all cheat you will explode around 1000m. Thats Jool. Must have gotten mixed up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"camacju","CreatedById":207172,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-22T06:50:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah, with stacked service bays you can \u003Cem\u003Edefinitely\u003C/em\u003E do a sea level sundive\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Little_Kerbal","CreatedById":211277,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-22T13:30:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe\u0027ll have to try to fly to the sun as well.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Chryssalid 8492","CreatedById":197332,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-25T13:36:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis was my first dive bomb into Kerbol.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://1drv.ms/v/s!Aoo6szyB84IXhiqIXsgLJ4P3RRKn?e=WyKonN\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://1drv.ms/v/s!Aoo6szyB84IXhiqIXsgLJ4P3RRKn?e=WyKonN\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhode_Enterprise_By-Matt","CreatedById":211240,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-25T15:40:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223960585\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201855\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619357812\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022197332\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Chryssalid 8492\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Chryssalid 8492 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis was my first dive bomb into Kerbol.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://1drv.ms/v/s!Aoo6szyB84IXhiqIXsgLJ4P3RRKn?e=WyKonN\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://1drv.ms/v/s!Aoo6szyB84IXhiqIXsgLJ4P3RRKn?e=WyKonN\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYikes! Exploded! Cool!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbalgod","CreatedById":211211,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-26T12:54:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncrashed\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tsar_bomba","CreatedById":196761,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-26T13:16:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait do they have to survive?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}